                            <comment id="13022596" author="yukim" created="Thu, 21 Apr 2011 02:27:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I got the same problem, and after making change in the statement like following&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;CREATE KEYSPACE CqlTest WITH strategy_class = SimpleStrategy AND strategy_options:replication_factor = 1;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;everything works fine.&lt;br/&gt;
(I&apos;m using apache-cassandra-2011-04-12_18-15-17 build version.)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think CQL doc should also be updated, because it states that &quot;replication_factor&quot; is required.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13022614" author="jbellis" created="Thu, 21 Apr 2011 05:06:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch to reject malformed keyspaces from cql.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(also patches CQL.textile docs source, but I have not yet figured out how to generate the html from that.)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13022763" author="jbellis" created="Thu, 21 Apr 2011 14:24:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;opened &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2526&quot; title=&quot;Add ant support to generate CQL documentation from textile source&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-2526&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-2526&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for doc generation&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
